Flock — Social Coordination Simplified
Flock is a real-time social coordination app that replaces the broken group chat planning process with structured decision-making. Create a flock, invite friends, vote on venues, match budgets anonymously, and go.
Live app: flockcrop.com

The Problem
Group chats turn into indecisive people, and they idk what to do loops. Someone suggests somewhere expensive. Two people go silent because they can't afford it but won't say so. The plan dies. Everyone stays home.
Flock fixes this with a structured coordination flow: create → invite → RSVP → vote → match budgets → confirm → go.
Core Features
Real-Time Coordination

Create flocks with time, date, and venue context
Invite friends and track RSVPs (going / maybe / declined)
Group venue voting with Google Places integration
Real-time messaging with typing indicators, emoji reactions, image sharing, and venue cards
Live location sharing within flocks

Anonymous Budget Matching

Every member privately submits their max budget — no one sees individual answers
Server computes the group spending ceiling (minimum of all submissions)
Venues above the group budget are hidden automatically
3-person minimum threshold protects anonymity
Individual submissions are deleted 24 hours after the flock completes

AI Crowd Intelligence

Real-time crowd predictions for venues using Google Places data, OpenWeatherMap, and time pattern analysis
Scores venues 0–100 with confidence ratings
12-hour hourly forecast, capacity estimates, wait times, best time to visit
Quieter alternative venue suggestions
Learning loop: user feedback after hangouts calibrates future predictions

Bill Splitting + Venmo Settlement

Post-hangout bill split with equal or custom amounts
Tip calculator (15% / 18% / 20% / custom)
Venmo deep-link settlement — one tap opens Venmo pre-filled with the correct amount and recipient
Ghost Mode pre-commitment — lock in your share before arriving to reduce flaking
No payment processing, no APIs, no transaction fees

Social Layer

Friend system with QR code sharing and phone-based discovery
Direct messages with venue cards, voting, pinning, replies, and reactions
24-hour expiring stories
User profiles with image upload

Safety

Trusted emergency contacts management
One-tap SOS alert sends GPS location to all contacts via email (Resend)
Real-time location sharing within flocks and DMs


